com.foreach.across.modules.bootstrapui.styles

Class AcrossBootstrapStyles

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.foreach.across.modules.bootstrapui.styles.AcrossBootstrapStyles

  • public class AcrossBootstrapStyles
extends Object
    Framework alternative for BootstrapStyles that offers customized bootstrap utility classes. These utility classes are the same as their bootstrap variant, except for: - having a prefix axu - removal of !important
    Since:
    3.0.0
    Author:
    Steven Gentens
